{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      FC as view layer only — our toolbar stays (Recommended)\n      Replace only CalendarGrid and its sub-components with a FullCalendar wrapper. The custom CalendarToolbar (Today / prev / next / Week–Month toggle), CalendarPagination, and URL state are untouched. PlanCalendarPage passes the current date range to FC via an imperative ref call. FC fires eventDrop → mutation and dateClick → quick-create.\n      \n        Pros\n          Smallest blast radius — plans 1 & 2 untouched\n          URL state stays as authoritative source of truth\n          Our toolbar design matches the rest of the app\n          Pagination logic stays unchanged\n        \n        Cons\n          Need to keep FC in sync via imperative calendarRef API\n          FC's own date-navigation must be disabled (headerToolbar={false})","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1780583562609}
